name: Satellite Doge-1 Mission
description: Satellite Doge-1 is a meme cryptocurrency token on Ethereum network.This idea is brought to life through mission to send Satellite Doge-1 into space.The Doge-1 cryptocurrency aims to be used for space related trading in the future. The project's aim is to create a lasting legacy in the crypto world by marrying the popular Dogecoin meme with a mission to reach the stars. Satellite Doge-1 has a total supply of 1 billion tokens. A 1% tax is applied to transactions, and these funds are allocated to support the development and growth of the project.
